(ns farsund.data.subs
  (:require [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [com.rpl.specter :as sp]
            [farsund.data.query :as q]
            [farsund.data.categories :as data.categories]))

(rf/reg-sub
  :data/search-value
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:data :search-value])))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/tmp-search-value
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:data :tmp-search-value])))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/search-updating?
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:data :search-updating?])))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/categories
  (fn [db _]
    (sp/select-one [:data :categories] db)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/parent-categories
  :<- [:data/categories]
  (fn [categories]
    (data.categories/parents categories)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/category-ancestors
  :<- [:data/categories]
  (fn [categories [_ id]]
    (data.categories/ancestors id categories)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/category-name
  :<- [:data/categories]
  (fn [categories [_ id]]
    (->> categories
         (filter (fn [[key _]] (= id key)))
         (first)
         (second))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/category-full-name
  :<- [:data/categories]
  (fn [categories [_ id]]
    (data.categories/full-name id " - " categories)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/market-report
  (fn [db _]
    (sp/select-one [:data :market-report] db)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/market-report.search
  (fn [db [_ value]]
    (sp/select [:data :market-report sp/ALL
                #(or (re-find (re-pattern value) (:name %))
                     (re-find (re-pattern value) (:ean %)))] db)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/product-stock
  (fn [db _]
    (sp/select-one [:data :product-stock] db)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/cg-data
  (fn [db _]
    (sp/select-one [:data :cg-data] db)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/market-order
  (fn [db _]
    (sp/select-one [:data :market-order] db)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/market-order.nth
  (fn [db [_ idx]]
    ;(get-in db [:data :market-order idx])
    (sp/select-one [:data :market-order idx] db)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/market-order.search
  (fn [db _]
    (let [search-value (get-in db [:data :search-value])]
      (sp/select [:data :market-order sp/ALL
                  #(or (re-find (re-pattern search-value) (:name %))
                       (re-find (re-pattern search-value) (:ean %)))] db))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/market-order.search.count
  :<- [:data/market-order.search]
  (fn [market-order _]
    (count market-order)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/market-order.search.nth
  :<- [:data/market-order.search]
  (fn [market-order [_ i]]
    (sp/select-one i market-order)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/market-order.count
  :<- [:data/market-order]
  (fn [market-order _]
    (count market-order)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/selected-categories
  (fn [db _]
    (or (sp/select-one [:data :settings :categories] db) [])))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/category-selected?
  :<- [:data/selected-categories]
  (fn [categories [_ category]]
    (contains? (set categories) category)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/min-pace
  (fn [db _]
    (or (sp/select-one [:data :settings :min-pace] db) 0.0)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/pace-period
  (fn [db _]
    (or (sp/select-one [:data :settings :pace-period] db) "day")))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/min-margin
  (fn [db _]
    (or (sp/select-one [:data :settings :min-margin] db) 0.0)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/mm-file-list
  (fn [db _]
    (or (sp/select-one [:data :mm-file-list] db) [])))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/show-ftp-files-dialog?
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:data :ui :show-ftp-files-dialog?] false)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/market-filtered-order
  :<- [:data/market-order]
  :<- [:data/selected-categories]
  :<- [:data/min-pace]
  :<- [:data/min-margin]
  (fn [[order categories min-pace min-margin :as params]]
    (apply q/order->market-order params)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/market-filtered-order.nth
  :<- [:data/market-filtered-order]
  (fn [order [_ idx]]
    (when (> (count order) idx) (nth order idx))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/market-filtered-order.count
  :<- [:data/market-filtered-order]
  (fn [order _]
    (count order)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/cg-filtered-order
  :<- [:data/market-order]
  :<- [:data/selected-categories]
  :<- [:data/min-pace]
  :<- [:data/min-margin]
  (fn [[order categories min-pace min-margin :as params]]
    (apply q/order->cg-order params)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/cg-filtered-order.nth
  :<- [:data/cg-filtered-order]
  (fn [order [_ idx]]
    (when (> (count order) idx) (nth order idx))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :data/cg-filtered-order.count
  :<- [:data/cg-filtered-order]
  (fn [order _]
    (count order)))
